Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.29,0:00:04.52,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Pocket Monsters New Year Special!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.06,0:00:08.73,Main,Narrator,220,0,0,,Visiting TV Tokyo today...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.73,0:00:11.93,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,...are Liko, Roy, \N and Captain Pikachu.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.93,0:00:14.27,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,And why are they here?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.07,0:00:23.24,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,What a surprise! They’re here to have the stars \N of popular shows take on{attempt} a rap challenge!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:17.07,0:00:23.24,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}What a surprise! They’re here to have the stars of popular shows take on{attempt} a rap challenge!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.34,0:00:26.04,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Could this be it, Roy?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:24.34,0:00:26.04,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Could this be it, Roy?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.04,0:00:28.15,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,I hear there’s someone amazing here.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:26.04,0:00:28.15,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}I hear there’s someone amazing here.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.15,0:00:29.45,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:28.15,0:00:28.95,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,502)\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.45,0:00:30.81,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Let’s just go in and check it out!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.81,0:00:31.62,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.45,0:00:35.49,Main,Liko/Roy,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.45,0:00:39.12,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,Whoa, amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.12,0:00:41.49,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,Whoa, it’s a real Pikachu!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:39.12,0:00:41.49,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Whoa, it’s a real Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.49,0:00:42.73,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:41.49,0:00:42.73,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Hello!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.73,0:00:43.69,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:42.73,0:00:43.69,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Hello!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.69,0:00:44.50,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.50,0:00:45.16,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.16,0:00:48.07,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, pleased to be here.{please treat me kindly.}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.00,0:00:52.57,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Attempting to rap will be \N Degawa Tetsurou-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.57,0:00:55.24,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,And doesn’t that outfit look familiar?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.07,0:00:57.11,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I’m Liko!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.11,0:00:58.28,Main,Degawa,0,0,100,,{\an8}Oh, Liko-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.34,0:00:58.41,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Pleased to be here.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.41,0:00:59.81,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,Pleased to be here.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.81,0:01:02.45,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,And I’m... Roy!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.45,0:01:04.05,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,Roy-kun, Liko-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.31,0:01:04.05,Main,Roy,0,0,100,,{\an8}Yep.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.05,0:01:05.02,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,Liko-kun, Roy-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.02,0:01:06.05,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Oh, it’s Liko-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.05,0:01:07.02,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,Oh, Liko-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.02,0:01:09.62,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,Liko-chan, Roy-kun. Pleased to be here!{this might sound silly to repeat at this point, but... also it’s the third time he’s said it and it’s after a bit of comedic confusion so hopefully it holds up fine -ed}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.45,0:01:09.62,Main,Roy,0,0,100,,{\an8}Roy-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.62,0:01:12.96,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,And... Next to me is...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.96,0:01:14.69,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Captain Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.69,0:01:18.63,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,Whoa! Amazing! It’s a real Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.63,0:01:20.40,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.40,0:01:21.47,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,I’ve been wondering...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.47,0:01:21.97,Main,Liko & Degawa,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.97,0:01:25.44,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,What’s that you’ve got?\N That, uh... hat?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.44,0:01:28.21,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,Oh, this? It’s my Watermelon Helmet...
Dialogue: 9,0:01:25.94,0:01:28.21,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Oh, this? It’s my Watermelon Helmet...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.21,0:01:29.91,Main,Roy,0,0,100,,{\an8}Watermelon Helmet...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.21,0:01:34.68,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,See, I always appear on this show \N called “Could You Charge My Bike?”...
Dialogue: 9,0:01:28.21,0:01:34.68,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}See, I always appear on this show \N called “Could You Charge My Bike?”...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.68,0:01:37.08,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,Where I wear this watermelon...
Dialogue: 9,0:01:34.68,0:01:37.08,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Where I wear this watermelon...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.08,0:01:38.12,Main,Liko,0,0,100,,{\an8}Ooh!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.08,0:01:38.92,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Ooh! It’s cute!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.92,0:01:39.48,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.48,0:01:42.72,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,And I travel around \N on an electric bike!
Dialogue: 9,0:01:40.05,0:01:42.72,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}And I travel around \N on an electric bike!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.72,0:01:45.02,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Ooh! That sounds fun!
Dialogue: 9,0:01:42.72,0:01:45.02,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Ooh! That sounds fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.72,0:01:45.02,Main,Roy,0,0,100,,{\an8}Ooh! An electric bike!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.02,0:01:46.96,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,Then when it runs out of power,
Dialogue: 9,0:01:45.02,0:01:45.69,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Then when it runs out of power,
Dialogue: 9,0:01:46.26,0:01:46.29,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Then {\alpha&HFF&}when it runs out of power,
Dialogue: 9,0:01:46.29,0:01:46.32,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Then when it runs out of power,
Dialogue: 9,0:01:46.32,0:01:46.36,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Then when it ru{\alpha&HFF&}ns out of power,
Dialogue: 9,0:01:46.36,0:01:46.39,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Then when it runs o{\alpha&HFF&}ut of power,
Dialogue: 9,0:01:46.39,0:01:46.42,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Then when it runs out {\alpha&HFF&}of power,
Dialogue: 9,0:01:46.42,0:01:46.46,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Then when it runs out of p{\alpha&HFF&}ower,
Dialogue: 9,0:01:46.46,0:01:46.49,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Then when it runs out of po{\alpha&HFF&}wer,
Dialogue: 9,0:01:46.49,0:01:46.52,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Then when it runs out of powe{\alpha&HFF&}r,
Dialogue: 9,0:01:46.52,0:01:46.96,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Then when it runs out of power,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.96,0:01:51.06,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,I borrow power from someone in town, \N have them charge it up,
Dialogue: 9,0:01:46.96,0:01:51.06,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}I borrow power from someone in town, \N have them charge it up,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.06,0:01:53.66,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,and continue my journey. \N That’s what the show’s about.{the kind of show it is.}
Dialogue: 9,0:01:51.06,0:01:53.66,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}and continue my journey. \N That’s what the show’s about.{the kind of show it is.}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.66,0:01:55.77,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,Oh! How about you guest on it sometime?
Dialogue: 9,0:01:54.43,0:01:55.77,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Oh! How about you guest on it sometime?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.77,0:01:57.67,Main,Liko/Roy,0,0,0,,What?! Can we?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.67,0:02:00.27,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,Can you ride an electric bike, Pikachu?
Dialogue: 9,0:01:57.67,0:02:00.27,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Can you ride an electric bike, Pikachu?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.11,0:02:03.67,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Couldn’t Pikachu recharge your bike?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.14,0:02:03.67,Main,Liko,0,0,100,,{\an8}Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.67,0:02:04.38,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.38,0:02:06.81,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,Pikachu’s a charger?!
Dialogue: 9,0:02:04.54,0:02:06.81,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Pikachu’s a charger?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.31,0:02:13.02,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Pikachu emits electricity, \N so he could recharge it!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.71,0:02:12.48,Main,Degawa,0,0,100,,{\an8}Oh! Really?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.48,0:02:13.02,Main,Degawa,0,0,100,,{\an8}Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.02,0:02:15.69,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,You’re perfect! Be a guest!
Dialogue: 9,0:02:14.49,0:02:15.69,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}You’re perfect! Be a guest!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.42,0:02:17.49,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,Pikachu!
Dialogue: 9,0:02:16.42,0:02:17.49,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.49,0:02:20.46,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,You’d be a perfect guest for my show!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.46,0:02:22.76,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,Pikachu, you should \N come ‘round sometime!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.46,0:02:32.34,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,“Degawa Tetsurou’s Could You Charge My Bike?” \N is a popular show that’s been running for seven years.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.34,0:02:37.67,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Degawa-san, who’s quite popular with kids, \Ngoes on a bizarre road trip!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.44,0:02:43.11,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,And Liko, Roy, and Cap \N have a request for Degawa-san!
Dialogue: 9,0:02:38.44,0:02:43.11,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}And Liko, Roy, and Cap \N have a request for Degawa-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.88,0:02:52.52,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Degawa-san, we’re here today to \N help you learn to like Pokémon more.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.52,0:02:57.43,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,We have a song called \N RVR: Rising Voltteccers Rap.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:53.42,0:02:57.43,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,0)\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}We have a song called \N RVR: Rising Voltteccers Rap.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.43,0:02:58.56,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 9,0:02:57.43,0:02:58.56,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}What is that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.56,0:03:01.17,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Would you try our rap challenge?
Dialogue: 9,0:02:58.56,0:03:01.17,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Would you try our rap challenge?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.17,0:03:03.03,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,Oh, so that’s the rap song?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.03,0:03:03.83,Main,Liko,0,0,100,,{\an8}Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.33,0:03:04.67,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,Gotcha, gotcha.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.67,0:03:06.54,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,I {\i1}can{\i0} rap a little, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.54,0:03:07.97,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.14,0:03:07.97,Main,Degawa,0,0,100,,{\an8}Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.51,0:03:10.54,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,And so, coming up...
Dialogue: 9,0:03:08.51,0:03:10.54,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}And so, coming up...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.54,0:03:14.58,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,A spectacular New Year lineup of \N special guests try the rap challenge!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:10.54,0:03:14.58,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}A spectacular New Year lineup of \N special guests try the rap challenge!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.18,0:03:16.48,Main,Left Miki,0,0,0,,Psychokinesis!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:15.18,0:03:16.48,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Psychokinesis!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.18,0:03:23.42,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Plus, a special edition of \N Professor Friede’s Pokémon Seminar!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.42,0:03:27.69,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,How many questions \N can {\i1}you{\i0} answer in this special quiz?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.13,0:03:32.43,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,All right, \N go ahead with the opening theme!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.13,0:03:35.63,Main,yama,0,0,0,,Everyone watching \N the Pocket Monsters anime.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.63,0:03:36.53,Main,yama,0,0,0,,I’m Yama.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.53,0:03:37.80,Main,Botchi,0,0,0,,I’m BotchiBoromaru!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.80,0:03:42.67,Main,yama,0,0,0,,Today, we’ve got a special live version for you, \N different from the usual opening.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.67,0:03:46.14,Main,Botchi,0,0,0,,Everybody sing along and get fired up!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.14,0:03:47.88,Main,yama,0,0,0,,Well then, please enjoy...
