Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.74,0:07:38.68,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,Oh, there’s a Pokémon \N named Koratta-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.68,0:07:39.24,Main,Liko/Roy,0,0,0,,That’s right!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.24,0:07:40.18,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,And one named Ratta-kun?
