Dialogue: 9,0:07:43.15,0:07:44.21,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Time for take two.
Comment: 10,0:07:44.21,0:07:45.15,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Oh!
