Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.53,0:08:39.94,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, a lot of fun... \N But are you sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.94,0:08:42.04,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,If it was bad, I could do a take three.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:40.14,0:08:42.04,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}If it was bad, I could do a take three.
