Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.82,0:08:55.59,Main,Degawa,0,0,0,,It’s just as interesting \N as Pokémon, so check it out!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.09,0:09:01.12,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I hear there’s someone amazing in this room!
Dialogue: 9,0:08:58.09,0:09:01.12,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}I hear there’s someone amazing in this room!
