Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.49,0:09:04.56,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,What if it’s a Gym Leader?!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:02.49,0:09:04.56,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}What if it’s a Gym Leader?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.10,0:09:07.46,Main,Liko/Roy,0,0,0,,Excuse us!
