Dialogue: 9,0:09:10.10,0:09:11.10,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.87,0:09:11.94,Main,Wentz,0,0,100,,{\an8}Liko-chan! Roy-kun!
