Dialogue: 9,0:09:11.10,0:09:12.60,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Hello!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.60,0:09:14.14,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.14,0:09:16.31,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,He’s so cute...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.27,0:09:20.48,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The next famous face is Wentz Eiji-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.38,0:09:24.65,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,On “Learn The News In 60 Seconds,”
Dialogue: 9,0:09:22.38,0:09:24.65,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}On “Learn The News In 60 Seconds,”
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.65,0:09:29.32,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,he’s the MC that makes \N the latest news simple to understand!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:24.65,0:09:29.32,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}he’s the MC that makes \N the latest news simple to understand!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.32,0:09:32.79,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,I’m Wentz Eiji, \N and I’ve started playing Pokémon lately.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.79,0:09:34.69,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,Pleased to have you!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.69,0:09:36.53,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,26 years ago...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:34.69,0:09:36.53,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}26 years ago...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.53,0:09:41.93,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,I was a really busy elementary schooler, \N so I never played it.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:36.53,0:09:41.93,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}I was a really busy elementary schooler, \N so I never played it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.93,0:09:44.23,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,A pretty {\i1}famous{\i0} \N busy elementary schooler, at that.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.23,0:09:44.87,Main,Liko/Roy,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.87,0:09:49.17,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,I didn’t play it back then, \N but I’ve picked it up now that I’m an adult!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:47.04,0:09:49.17,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}I didn’t play it back then, \N but I’ve picked it up now that I’m an adult!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.17,0:09:51.24,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Wow! That’s lovely!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:49.17,0:09:51.24,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Wow! That’s lovely!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.17,0:09:52.08,Main,Roy,0,0,100,,{\an8}Ooh! That so, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.08,0:09:55.01,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Wentz-san, \N have a look at our Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.01,0:09:58.68,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,He’s the ship captain \N of our adventuring ship!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.68,0:10:00.78,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,His name’s Captain Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.78,0:10:02.79,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,Captain Pikachu! \N Pleased to have you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.79,0:10:06.62,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,So, if he’s the ship captain, \N he gives the orders, right?
Dialogue: 9,0:10:02.79,0:10:06.62,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}So, if he’s the ship captain, \N he gives the orders, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.62,0:10:08.06,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Yeah! Of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.03,0:10:12.86,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,{\q2}Then, if you would... \N Decide the future of entertainer Wentz Eiji, too!{Then if you would, decide the future of this entertainer Wentz Eiji, too...}
Dialogue: 9,0:10:09.03,0:10:12.86,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Then, if you would... \N Decide the future of entertainer Wentz Eiji, too!{Then if you would, decide the future of this entertainer Wentz Eiji, too...}
