Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.17,0:10:20.24,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,Huh, you will?!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:19.17,0:10:20.24,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Huh, you will?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.07,0:10:22.61,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,That response {\i1}seemed{\i0} like a yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.94,0:10:23.64,Main,Roy,0,0,100,,{\an8}What? Cap, you can do that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.61,0:10:24.98,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,Okay then, I’ll have to hear him out later.
