Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.21,0:11:01.48,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Well then, \N let the rap challenge begin!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.48,0:11:04.75,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,This one is harder than last time!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.75,0:11:06.45,Main,Liko,0,0,190,,Let’s learn about more and more!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.45,0:11:08.65,Main,Liko,0,0,190,,Pokémon with “don” in their names!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.65,0:11:10.49,Main,Liko,0,0,190,,Let’s have Roy show us how it’s done!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.49,0:11:12.46,Main,Liko,0,0,190,,3! 2! 1! Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.46,0:11:14.46,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Saidon, Yadon, Donmel, Groudon,
