Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.28,0:11:40.18,Main,Liko/Roy,0,0,0,,Oh, are you okay?
Dialogue: 9,0:11:39.28,0:11:40.18,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Oh, are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.18,0:11:41.15,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 9,0:11:40.18,0:11:41.15,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.15,0:11:43.05,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,What do you think, Pikachu? \N Did I do good?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.45,0:11:47.62,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,Oh, he just gave me \N a good{hard} slap on the butt!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.62,0:11:50.76,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,You really put some muscle \N into that! Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.76,0:11:52.43,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,Did I do good? Was it okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.70,0:11:53.80,Main,Liko,0,0,100,,{\an8}Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.43,0:11:54.00,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,You were really cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.80,0:11:55.13,Main,Liko,0,0,100,,{\an8}Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.00,0:11:55.13,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.70,0:11:57.90,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,Honestly... Feel my heart.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:56.80,0:11:57.90,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Honestly... Feel my heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.90,0:11:58.67,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Huh? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 9,0:11:57.90,0:11:58.67,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Huh? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.67,0:12:00.07,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,It’s pounding away fiercely.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:58.67,0:12:00.07,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}It’s pounding away fiercely.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.07,0:12:01.44,Main,Liko,0,0,100,,{\an8}Really?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.07,0:12:02.97,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,You’re right, it is!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:00.07,0:12:02.97,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}You’re right, it is!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.44,0:12:03.94,Main,Wentz,0,0,100,,{\an8}I was really nervous.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.94,0:12:07.38,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Wentz-san, did you enjoy \N our rap challenge?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.84,0:12:09.68,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,I’m starting to enjoy it {\i1}now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.41,0:12:12.88,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,Almost think I should’ve \N rapped {\i1}before{\i0} we chatted...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.62,0:12:14.58,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,It was great.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.58,0:12:18.05,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,Feeling nervous, \N but then overcoming it... That feels great.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:15.62,0:12:18.05,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Feeling nervous, \N but then overcoming it... That feels great.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.05,0:12:19.52,Main,Liko/Roy,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:18.05,0:12:19.52,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.52,0:12:25.36,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,{\q2}This is Learn The News In 60 Seconds, so next, how about you \N try and explain what makes Pokémon brilliant in 60 seconds?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:22.36,0:12:25.36,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}This is Learn The News In 60 Seconds, so next, how about you \N try and explain what makes Pokémon brilliant in 60 seconds?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.13,0:12:27.76,Main,Liko/Roy,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.30,0:12:29.60,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,Makes you nervous, right?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:28.30,0:12:29.60,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Makes you nervous, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.53,0:12:35.81,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,Wednesdays at 9 PM. \N Learn The News In 60 Seconds.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:31.97,0:12:35.81,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\fad(281,0)\q2\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Wednesdays at 9 PM. \N Learn The News In 60 Seconds.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.47,0:12:37.74,Main,Wentz,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:36.47,0:12:37.74,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.94,0:12:42.61,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,So far, there’s been \N one success and one failure!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:39.94,0:12:42.61,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}So far, there’s been \N one success and one failure!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.61,0:12:45.18,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The last one is the hardest rap verse...
Dialogue: 9,0:12:42.61,0:12:45.18,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}The last one is the hardest rap verse...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.18,0:12:50.09,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,But before that, \N we have another special segment{corner} for you!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:45.18,0:12:50.09,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}But before that, \N we have another special segment{corner} for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.09,0:12:51.29,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Friede here.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:50.82,0:12:51.29,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\q2\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Friede here.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.29,0:12:53.62,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,It’s time for my Pokémon Seminar!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:51.29,0:12:53.62,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}It’s time for my Pokémon Seminar!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.29,0:12:58.13,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Today, it’s a special edition!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:55.29,0:12:58.13,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Today, it’s a special edition!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.23,0:13:02.33,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,We’ll be taking a look at our adventures \N as the Rising Voltteccers,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.33,0:13:05.44,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,and the Pokémon \N we’ve met along the way.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.74,0:13:16.21,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,{\q2}Our adventure began when we met a Paldean girl \N named Liko, who had enrolled at Sekiei Academy.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.45,0:13:24.72,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,{\q2}The mysterious pendant Liko got from her grandma \N prompted a suspicious organization to chase after her...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.32,0:13:29.73,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,That’s right. The Explorers.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.73,0:13:34.26,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Their goals are unclear, \N but they’re after Liko’s pendant.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.30,0:13:37.63,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Found you!{001}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.34,0:13:52.18,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,{\q2}We, the Rising Voltteccers, came to Sekiei Academy \N to save Liko and her pendant from the Explorers.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.18,0:13:54.35,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh? Lizardon?!{002}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.98,0:14:01.39,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,{\q2}On our adventures, we met a boy \N who dreamed of becoming a Pokémon Trainer: Roy!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.76,0:14:06.83,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,And his personal treasure was none other \N than an Ancient Monster Ball.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.07,0:14:11.50,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,And now for a question!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.50,0:14:14.94,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,{\an8}A Pokémon popped out of that ball,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.94,0:14:18.41,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,{\an8}but do you know which Pokémon it was?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.71,0:14:29.62,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,{\an8}Liko’s pendant shone out, \N resonating with the Ancient Monster Ball!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.29,0:14:32.82,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,{\an8}Then, out of it came...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.87,0:14:48.91,Main,Friede,0,0,180,,That’s right! The answer is... \N the black Rekkuuza!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.74,0:14:54.44,Main,Friede,0,0,180,,Yeah. It shocked me too.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.01,0:14:58.55,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Well then, \N let’s continue with our adventure.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.55,0:15:02.82,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,We even went to the Wild Area together!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.59,0:15:10.99,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,The Wild Area is home to many more Pokémon \N than any other place in the Galar Region!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.53,0:15:14.00,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,{\an8}And now, time for a question!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.00,0:15:19.80,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,{\an8}We ate a certain meal in the Wild Area, \N and everybody loved it, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.80,0:15:21.91,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,{\an8}Do you know what that meal was?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.67,0:15:26.68,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,{\an8}There’s a lot of Momon Berries here.{027}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.68,0:15:28.68,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,{\an8}...makes it taste a lot better.{027 (partial line)}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.05,0:15:31.45,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,{\an8}Two: The berries!{027}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.45,0:15:33.85,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,{\an8}Three: The heating!{027}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.68,0:15:38.56,Main,Friede,0,0,180,,That’s right! The answer is... curry!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.36,0:15:45.26,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Liko and Roy put their hearts \N into making it for Dot,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.26,0:15:48.43,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,who’d never tasted curry \N nor been interested in food.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.03,0:15:53.14,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Dot usually keeps away from others,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.14,0:15:58.04,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,but eating curry together \N strengthened her bond with her friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.94,0:16:00.78,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.02,0:16:08.18,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Cap gives them a perfect score!{027}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.18,0:16:09.65,Main,Liko & Roy,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.96,0:16:15.43,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.43,0:16:21.73,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,{\q2}We, the Rising Voltteccers, are a team{chiimu} of adventurers \N pursuing the mysteries of Pokémon and the world.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.13,0:16:28.07,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,And the captain of our airship \N is none other than Cap, a.k.a. Captain Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.67,0:16:36.21,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now for a question! There’s something \N Cap can do that other Pikachu cannot.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.21,0:16:38.41,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,{\an8}So, everybody, do you know what it is?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.83,0:16:58.87,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,No way!{018}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.87,0:17:03.51,Main,Friede,0,0,180,,That’s right! The answer is... \N He can fly!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.58,0:17:08.31,Main,Friede,0,0,180,,That was how I met my partner Cap.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.31,0:17:13.22,Main,Friede,0,0,180,,And it was also the moment \N the Rising Voltteccers were born.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.28,0:17:15.99,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Whoa!{018 (partial line)}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.99,0:17:18.19,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,This really is the best!{018}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.09,0:17:23.59,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Well then, let’s continue with our adventure.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.79,0:17:29.07,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,When we headed to the Galar Mine \N in search of the black Rekkuuza,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.07,0:17:34.24,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,we met none other than Galarian Fire, \N one of the Six Hero Pokémon!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.67,0:17:39.11,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Galarian Fire’s fiercely burning rage \N had us in quite a bind!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.58,0:17:43.01,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,But... It’s time for a question!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.01,0:17:48.52,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,{\an8}Liko’s pendant shone out, \N and it transformed into a mysterious Pokémon.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.52,0:17:52.76,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,{\an8}But you know that Pokémon’s name, right?{Trick question it’s Kodaikame! -TL}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.17,0:18:07.27,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,{\an8}But the pendant turned into \N this little one.{024}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.27,0:18:10.24,Main,Diana,0,0,0,,{\an8}This little one looks like a Terapagos.{024}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.24,0:18:11.34,Main,Terapagos,0,0,0,,Terapagos?{024}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.34,0:18:14.58,Main,Friede,0,0,180,,The answer is... Terapagos!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.01,0:18:19.38,Main,Friede,0,0,180,,I was shocked when that pendant \N turned into a Pokémon!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.32,0:18:26.36,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Calming its anger, \N Galarian Fire decided to come with us.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.36,0:18:31.16,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,And the awakened Terapagos \N came along on our adventure, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.40,0:18:35.90,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Diana-san is an adventurer,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.90,0:18:41.37,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,{\q2}and she taught us about the Ancient Adventurer Lucius, \N and about Terapagos, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.51,0:18:46.91,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Terapagos’s wish is to go \N to the paradise known as Rakua.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.41,0:18:53.28,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,To fulfill that wish, we need to seek \N the Six Hero Pokémon who traveled with Lucius.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.75,0:19:02.56,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,{\q2}The Pokémon from the Six Heroes traveling with us now \N are Oliva, Galarian Fire, and Laplace.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.06,0:19:09.43,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Which leaves Basagiri, Entei, \N and the black Rekkuuza as the remaining three.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.30,0:19:17.71,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Yeah! Just {\i1}thinking{\i0} about finding Pokémon \N nobody’s ever seen before fills you with excitement!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.08,0:19:23.31,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,And if you’re getting excited \N about Pokémon you’ve never seen before...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.31,0:19:27.38,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Then to conclude this seminar, \N take a look at this Pokémon.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.95,0:19:31.82,Main,Friede,0,0,280,,Your hint is this \N characteristic silhouette...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.82,0:19:35.19,Main,Friede,0,0,280,,But do you know \N what this Pokémon is called?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.06,0:19:38.19,Main,Friede,0,0,280,,See the answer after the commercials!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.73,0:19:46.30,Main,Friede,0,0,280,,And now, the answer is...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.64,0:19:49.57,Main,Friede,0,0,280,,The Metalsmith Pokémon, Kanuchan!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.44,0:19:55.81,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,A Pokémon that creates \N her very own original hammer.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.81,0:20:00.62,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Never stopping until she’s satisfied... \N She’s got a craftsman’s mindset!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.55,0:20:03.82,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Will we meet one \N in our future adventures?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.82,0:20:05.39,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,I can’t wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.79,0:20:11.59,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Whoops! \N It’s about time we said farewell.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.13,0:20:15.87,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,But you’ve all gotten closer to being \N Pokémon Professors today, haven’t you?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.87,0:20:17.13,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Isn’t that right, Cap?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.00,0:20:24.51,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Now, let’s plot a course \N heading for new adventures!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.04,0:20:28.44,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.05,0:20:35.62,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\an8}Friede and the Rising Voltteccers embark \N on adventures seeking the rest of the Six Heroes.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.15,0:20:43.83,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\an8}And... Liko and Roy have delightful encounters \N with Pokémon they’ve never seen before!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.33,0:20:49.40,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Not Nyahoja too!{036}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.40,0:20:51.90,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself!{036}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.90,0:20:54.90,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Sing out nice and loud!{Roysong}{037}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.90,0:20:58.17,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Meguroco! Waruvile! Waruvial!{Roysong}{037}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.17,0:21:00.18,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Who will we meet next?!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:58.54,0:21:00.18,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\fad(850,0)\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Who will we meet next?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.18,0:21:01.24,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I can’t wait to find out!
Dialogue: 9,0:21:00.18,0:21:01.24,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}I can’t wait to find out!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.78,0:21:00.91,Main,Roy,0,0,100,,{\an8}Right?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.24,0:21:02.01,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,You said it!
Dialogue: 9,0:21:01.24,0:21:02.01,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}You said it!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.01,0:21:02.75,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 9,0:21:02.01,0:21:02.75,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.75,0:21:04.35,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,So, you think they’re in here?
Dialogue: 9,0:21:02.75,0:21:04.35,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}So, you think they’re in here?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.35,0:21:05.28,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:04.35,0:21:05.28,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.61,0:21:05.85,Main,Roy,0,0,100,,{\an8}Should we open the door?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.28,0:21:06.72,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Let’s do it!
Dialogue: 9,0:21:05.28,0:21:06.72,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Let’s do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.72,0:21:07.42,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.42,0:21:09.69,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Whoa! What is this place?! \N It’s amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.95,0:21:09.69,Main,Liko,0,0,100,,{\an8}Amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.69,0:21:11.15,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,They’re here, they’re here, \N they’re here!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.56,0:21:13.49,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Here they are!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.49,0:21:14.42,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.42,0:21:15.12,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.12,0:21:16.23,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.23,0:21:18.19,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Yeah, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.19,0:21:19.03,Main,Right Miki,0,0,0,,It’s Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.03,0:21:20.50,Main,Both Miki,0,0,0,,Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.53,0:21:24.80,Main,Right Miki,0,0,0,,Hey... You can’t say that \N this early in the morning!
Dialogue: 9,0:21:23.33,0:21:24.80,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Hey... You can’t say that \N this early in the morning!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.80,0:21:25.50,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 9,0:21:24.80,0:21:25.50,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.50,0:21:28.14,Main,Roy,0,0,230,,You can understand \N what Pikachu’s saying?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.17,0:21:28.57,Main,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)\c0\3c&HFFFFFF\fscx80\fscy80\blur4.5\pos(960,1057)}They dropped in straight after Oha Suta was broadcast live
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.84,0:21:28.14,Main,Left Miki,0,0,100,,{\an8}What did he say?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.57,0:21:29.81,Main,Right Miki,0,0,0,,What is it, Liko and Roy?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.81,0:21:32.98,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Um, could we ask your names?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.98,0:21:33.88,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,You don’t know us?!
Dialogue: 9,0:21:32.98,0:21:33.88,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}You don’t know us?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.88,0:21:34.81,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 9,0:21:33.88,0:21:34.81,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.81,0:21:35.78,Main,Liko/Roy,0,0,0,,W-We’re sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.78,0:21:37.28,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,It’s... our first time meeting...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.28,0:21:38.51,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Our first time meeting, huh...?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.51,0:21:40.08,Main,Right Miki,0,0,0,,Well then, \Nshall we introduce ourselves?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.08,0:21:40.62,Main,Left Miki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.62,0:21:42.22,Main,Right Miki,0,0,0,,We’re Miki.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.92,0:21:42.65,Main,Left Miki,0,0,100,,{\an8}Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.22,0:21:44.39,Main,Right Miki,0,0,0,,I’m the big brother, Mew.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.15,0:21:44.92,Main,Roy,0,0,100,,{\an8}Mew?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.39,0:21:46.22,Main,Left Miki,0,0,0,,And I’m Mewtwo.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.22,0:21:47.42,Main,Roy,0,0,100,,{\an8}Mewtwo?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.22,0:21:47.09,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Together, we’re...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.09,0:21:49.33,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Mew, Mewtwo, Mewtwo, Mew.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.33,0:21:50.13,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,That’s us.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.96,0:21:49.33,Main,Liko,0,0,100,,{\an8}They’re Pokémon?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.33,0:21:50.13,Main,Roy,0,0,100,,{\an8}Pokémon?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.13,0:21:51.29,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Here, of all places?!{Imagine finding them here!}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.29,0:21:52.30,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.93,0:21:54.30,Main,Left Miki,0,0,0,,Psychokinesis!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.77,0:21:59.20,Main,Right Miki,0,0,0,,Well, that’s enough \N joking around for now.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.20,0:21:59.80,Main,Left Miki,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.80,0:22:01.37,Main,Right Miki,0,0,0,,Sorry for dragging you into it.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.84,0:22:07.31,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Miki also appear \N on the kids show Oha Suta!
Dialogue: 9,0:22:02.84,0:22:07.31,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&}Miki also appear \N on the kids show Oha Suta!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.31,0:22:13.22,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\q2}The big brother Kousei-san and the little brother Asei-san \N make up a comedian brother duo!
Dialogue: 9,0:22:07.31,0:22:13.22,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&\q2}The big brother Kousei-san and the little brother Asei-san \N make up a comedian brother duo!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:14.12,0:22:15.38,Main,Right Miki,0,0,0,,So, what brings you here?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.38,0:22:20.79,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,We’re here today because \N we want you two to try rapping for us.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.79,0:22:21.62,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Rapping?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:21.62,0:22:22.43,Main,Liko/Roy,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.43,0:22:26.20,Main,Right Miki,0,0,0,,Huh? Sounds pretty tough. \N Rapping like in a song, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:26.20,0:22:27.06,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,That’s right!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.06,0:22:33.17,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,There’s this song called \N RVR: Rising Voltteccers Rap.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:33.17,0:22:36.21,Main,Left Miki,0,0,0,,No, big brother can sing \N Ketsumei-shi’s Friends.
Dialogue: 9,0:22:34.84,0:22:36.21,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&\q2}No, big brother can sing \N Ketsumei-shi’s Friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:36.21,0:22:37.67,Main,Liko/Roy,0,0,0,,Wrong song! Wrong song!
Dialogue: 9,0:22:36.21,0:22:37.67,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&\q2}Wrong song! Wrong song!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:37.67,0:22:39.68,Main,Right Miki,0,0,0,,You want me to sing that?
Dialogue: 9,0:22:37.67,0:22:39.68,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&\q2}You want me to sing that?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:40.74,0:22:43.21,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,It’s the hardest difficulty!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.21,0:22:47.32,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Everyone, \N give it a try along with Miki!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:47.32,0:22:48.92,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Well then, let’s get straight to it!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:48.92,0:22:50.02,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:48.92,0:22:49.59,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:49.59,0:22:50.89,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Rap challenge...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:50.89,0:22:52.02,Main,Liko/Roy,0,0,0,,Start!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:52.02,0:22:53.29,Main,Right Miki,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:53.92,0:22:55.42,Main,Roy,0,0,210,,Let’s learn about more and more!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:55.42,0:22:57.53,Main,Roy,0,0,210,,Next up, cheerful bird Pokémon!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:57.53,0:22:59.60,Main,Roy,0,0,210,,Let’s have Liko show us how it’s done!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:59.60,0:23:01.36,Main,Roy,0,0,210,,3! 2! 1! Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:01.36,0:23:03.30,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Perap raps, Ikirinko Uproars,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:03.30,0:23:05.33,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Kuwassu dances and the carnival starts!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:03.30,0:23:04.23,Main,Miki,0,0,100,,{\an8}She’s good.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:05.33,0:23:07.17,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,You two, sing together!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:07.17,0:23:08.37,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:08.37,0:23:08.90,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:08.90,0:23:11.07,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Hey! We’re Miki!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:11.07,0:23:13.01,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Kousei, Asei, that’s us!
Dialogue: 9,0:23:11.81,0:23:13.01,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\fad(314,0)\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&\q2}Kousei, Asei, that’s us!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:13.01,0:23:15.01,Main,Left Miki,0,0,0,,Perap raps, Ikirinko Uproars,
Dialogue: 9,0:23:13.01,0:23:15.01,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&\q2}Perap raps, Ikirinko Uproars,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:15.01,0:23:16.61,Main,Left Miki,0,0,0,,Kuwassu dances and the carnival starts!
Dialogue: 9,0:23:15.01,0:23:16.61,Main,Left Miki,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&\q2}Kuwassu dances and the carnival starts!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:16.61,0:23:17.75,Main,Right Miki,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 9,0:23:16.61,0:23:17.75,Main,Right Miki,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&\q2}Yay!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.75,0:23:18.41,Main,Left Miki,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:18.41,0:23:20.78,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Hold on, hold on, stop there!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:18.88,0:23:20.78,Main,Left Miki,0,0,100,,{\an8}I twowwy! I twowwy!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.78,0:23:22.18,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 9,0:23:21.02,0:23:22.18,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,0)\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&\q2}Wait, wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:22.18,0:23:22.99,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 9,0:23:22.18,0:23:22.99,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&\q2}Huh?
Comment: 10,0:23:20.85,0:23:22.52,Main,Left Miki,0,0,0,,I twowwy! I twowwy!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:22.99,0:23:25.35,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Wait, Big Bro, were you singing?
Dialogue: 9,0:23:22.99,0:23:23.39,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&\q2}Wait, Big Bro, were you singing?
Dialogue: 9,0:23:23.92,0:23:25.35,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&\q2}Wait, Big Bro, were you singing?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.22,0:23:26.79,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.79,0:23:29.19,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Huh? I feel like I didn’t hear \N the big bro’s voice...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:29.19,0:23:29.69,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:29.69,0:23:33.03,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,We’re brothers, \N so our voices were so synchronised...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:30.76,0:23:34.50,Main,Roy,0,0,100,,{\an8}We were hoping you’d both try it together...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:33.03,0:23:34.50,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,That was great and all, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:34.50,0:23:35.67,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Our voices sound too similar.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.16,0:23:36.57,Main,Miki,0,0,100,,{\an8}They’re too similar.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.67,0:23:36.57,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,It was a real surprise.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:36.57,0:23:39.64,Main,Left Miki,0,0,0,,Well, I could hear him \N going “Ah” quietly next to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:39.64,0:23:42.07,Main,Left Miki,0,0,0,,I heard him going “Ah, ah, ah”...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:42.07,0:23:43.04,Main,Left Miki,0,0,0,,He probably was singing, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:43.04,0:23:44.21,Main,Right Miki,0,0,0,,It was totally a “featuring” type thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:44.21,0:23:45.68,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Featuring... Featuring, yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:45.68,0:23:47.28,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Asei featuring Kousei.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:45.68,0:23:47.91,Main,Roy,0,0,100,,{\an8}Well then, I guess it counts...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:47.28,0:23:50.38,Main,Liko/Roy,0,0,0,,We’ll call it a success!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:50.38,0:23:51.55,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,We’re good?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:51.55,0:23:52.21,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:52.21,0:23:53.62,Main,Right Miki,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 9,0:23:52.48,0:23:53.62,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&\q2}Yay!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:52.92,0:23:53.62,Main,Miki,0,0,100,,{\an8}We did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:53.62,0:23:54.28,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 9,0:23:53.62,0:23:54.28,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&\q2}We did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:54.28,0:23:55.89,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,We did it, right, Pikachu?
Dialogue: 9,0:23:54.28,0:23:55.89,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord9\3c&HF6FBF6&\q2}We did it, right, Pikachu?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:57.02,0:23:57.99,Main,Right Miki,0,0,240,,How could you {\i1}say{\i0} that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:57.99,0:23:59.32,Main,Left Miki,0,0,240,,What is Pikachu saying?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:58.55,0:24:00.32,Main,Roy,0,0,100,,{\an8}What is he saying?! I wanna know!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:00.32,0:24:01.69,Main,Left Miki,0,0,0,,I wanna know!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:02.49,0:24:04.29,Main,Liko,0,0,210,,What did you think of today?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:04.29,0:24:05.70,Main,Right Miki,0,0,210,,Today was the best!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:04.73,0:24:05.70,Main,Left Miki,0,0,100,,{\an8}The best!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:05.70,0:24:08.70,Main,Right Miki,0,0,210,,Now I wanna watch Pokémon \N even more than before.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:08.70,0:24:10.10,Main,Right Miki,0,0,210,,I wanna see your progress.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.10,0:24:11.43,Main,Roy,0,0,210,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.63,0:24:12.44,Main,Liko,0,0,100,,{\an8}Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:11.43,0:24:13.27,Main,Roy,0,0,210,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.87,0:24:18.04,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\an8}Next time on \N the Pocket Monsters anime...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:19.28,0:24:22.31,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\an8}The Rising Voltteccers \N receive a job request.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.31,0:24:25.65,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\an8}Their job is to find a lost Pokémon.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:25.05,0:24:26.12,Main,Liko & Roy,0,0,210,,Anokusa!{035}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:26.12,0:24:27.55,Main,Hunterbosslady,0,0,210,,...will hurt \N all these Pokémon!{035}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:28.58,0:24:32.09,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\an8}But oh no! \N It turns into a kidnapping?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:32.66,0:24:35.89,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yet Friede and Cap \N can’t stop bickering{fighting}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:40.10,0:24:42.33,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Friede and Cap: The Duo in the Wilderness
Dialogue: 10,0:24:42.33,0:24:43.90,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Look forward to it!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:44.33,0:24:45.74,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Pocket Monsters...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:45.74,0:24:47.57,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,...was brought to you...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:47.57,0:24:49.11,Main,Liko/Roy,0,0,0,,...by these sponsors!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:49.11,0:24:50.47,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,That way!{035}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:51.37,0:24:52.84,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,That way!{035}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:55.51,0:24:59.08,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The mysterious Pokemon \N that awoke from the pendant, Terapagos!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:59.08,0:25:03.65,Main,Diana,0,0,0,,If you meet the remaining Six Heroes, \N I’m certain it will regain its original power. {Dread Terapagos}{026}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:03.65,0:25:07.09,Main,Diana,0,0,0,,That is when the path \N to Rakua will open.{026}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:07.09,0:25:11.23,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Liko and Roy trace a new course \N toward their dreams!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:11.23,0:25:13.20,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Rising Voltteccers...{026 (partial line)}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:13.20,0:25:14.60,Main,Everyone,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go!{\i0}{026}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:14.60,0:25:20.70,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\an8}TV anime Pocket Monsters! \N Airs weekly on Fridays at 6:55 PM!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:20.70,0:25:23.21,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,{\an8}With Pokémon by my side, \N I’ll do just fine!{026}
